      "chain_name": "Plaintext Password Dump \u2192 Forged Webhook \u2192 Transaction Fraud",
      "attack_scenario": "Attacker exfiltrates plaintext passwords via database access or a separate SQL injection, logs in as a seller to list items, and forges unsigned payment webhooks directly to the server to fake payment completion without transfer of actual money.",
